</p><note type="important" id="GUID-7215619B-4D8E-42B1-B219-10C1EF6B5FB5" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Do not lean on the strip support. 
</p></note><note id="GUID-65ABD6CE-CA7E-4D4C-BA15-BD5A20EDD97C" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">After the service visit: make sure you position the bracket in the original position. 
